message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper deals with deep learning methods applied to medical imaging problems, specifically transfer learning from ImageNet to kidney detection in ultrasound images. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of neural networks (cs.NEURON) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) in medical imaging. Finally, the paper specifically focuses on medical imaging (cs.MED) and its unique challenges, such as limited training data.
